This paper discusses the performance analysis of a mixed full and half duplex small cell network, which involves wireless communication and networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and communication theory, which suggests that cs.IT (Information Theory) is another likely category. The paper also discusses the area spectral efficiency, which is related to multimedia communication, indicating that cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category. The paper also involves system design and optimization, which suggests that cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category. Finally, the paper discusses interference and outage, which are related to security and cryptography, indicating that cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is another possible category.
